Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:29.94,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs24\frz-90\fn@方正大黑_GBK\b1\pos(176,129)}「{\fn@方正粗宋_GBK}海胜麟六{\fn@方正大黑_GBK}的送葬」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不像是你的作风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord0\b1\fs12\fn@宋体\frz-90\c&HFFFFFF&\move(79,206,91,206,0,390)\clip(84,170,156,240)}侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胜还是跟以往一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的推理之后蒙混过关
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.09,0:01:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an5\bord0\fn宋体\b1\fs13\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HFFFFFF&\move(28,192,44,192,0,430)\clip(33,88,138,279)}R.\NA.\NI.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.09,0:01:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\frz-90\an5\bord0\fn@宋体\b1\fs13\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HFFFFFF&\move(28,167,41,167,0,430)\clip(33,88,138,279)}人工智能（\h\h\h）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要使用电视转播这种方式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他无法在众目睽睽之下再做抵赖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这么不喜欢海胜麟六吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.78,0:01:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想让真相大白而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是本来就对真相很有兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因果说  你是为了他才成为侦探的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了了解人类的真实想法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才成为侦探的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是我唯一能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的真实想法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是灵魂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你与因果约定  一直为他提供灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才成为侦探的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在因果不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有必要再追求真相了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胜正在操纵别天王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以放任不管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（关东电视台）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord0.3\b1\be2\3a&H8D\fs12\fn@宋体\frz-90\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\fad(0,400)\move(507,193,519,193,0,360)\clip(512,145,575,255)}新任议员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在网络上广为流传的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假想影像之一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天  摧毁电视台的到底是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝大多数人认为是微波武器攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参考人  海胜麟六
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微波  电磁波本来就是眼睛无法看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微波供电的电力密度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大是23mW/cm2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顶多不会超过家用微波炉功率的百分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从Full  Circle流出的内部资料里指出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份资料是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据显示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事故发生地的数值高达几百万瓦特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不是微波炉的功率了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是耐久能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能与供电能力比较
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么复杂的东西我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是许多外国言论指出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经达到当做武器使用的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  JJ集团难道是武器制造商吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:04:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an5\bord0\b1\fs12\fn宋体\c&H000000&\move(103,143,115,143,0,520)\clip(109,100,154,227)}J\NJ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:04:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an5\bord0\b1\fs12\fn@宋体\frz-90\c&H000000&\move(103,180,115,180,0,520)\clip(109,100,154,227)}集团会长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2001年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人都看见了客机撞击五角大楼的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来却流传开大楼爆炸一说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还有人相信氢弹爆炸的荒谬说法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2011年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次灾难的影响至今还残留着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时至今日竟然还有人认为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次灾难是由地震武器造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord0\b1\fs12\fn@宋体\frz-90\c&HFFFFFF&\move(51,143,64,143,0,420)\clip(57,52,156,224)}海胜麟六的女儿  帮忙家事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  侦探先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们很容易相信真相被隐藏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  认为只有自己能够找寻到真相
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真相有无数个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而满足于眼前的「真相」的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是停止了继续思考罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别天王的力量  能扭曲真相吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没感觉到…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以隐藏真相也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你平时的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有隐藏什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视台演播室里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了神秘的爆炸事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:04:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那个时候海胜麟六走出了演播室门外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保住了一命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是事实不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果海胜没有去电视台的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胜梨江小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸那天你看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说海胜不在现场？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该是证明父亲清白的场合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨江  说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an5\bord0\b1\fs12\fn@宋体\frz-90\c&H000000&\move(375,177,389,177,0,420)\clip(381,84,483,274)}海胜家 女佣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个侦探相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不会说谎的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要回报他的信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在电视台爆炸之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到了爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:06:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在家里不代表就跟爆炸有关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我调阅了电视台的监视器录像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当天没有拍到海胜麟六先生的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是为了让人以为自己确实是在电视台里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而只是和相关人员统一了口径的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord0\b1\fs12\fn@宋体\frz-90\c&HFFFFFF&\move(504,158,518,158,0,400)\clip(510,98,599,223)}电视台制片人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当我是同犯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在安全的地方引爆炸弹也是有可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord0\b1\fs12\fn@宋体\frz-90\c&HFFFFFF&\move(230,148,245,148,0,420)\clip(235,55,327,262)}检察厅  联合调整部  检察官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反对  有异议
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.49,0:06:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是法院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an5\bord0\b1\fs12\fn@宋体\frz-90\c&HFFFFFF&\move(479,191,491,191,0,420)\clip(484,138,551,226)}助理侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事军队和警察正在一起调查爆炸原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还没有确认
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有找到携带式地对空导弹的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2001的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五角大楼不是被客机而是被导弹破坏的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这种阴谋论
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,供给公共保安队的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:07:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是所说的  精确定向导弹的部件之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战时的供给达到了600以上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不稀奇呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那情报什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说警察捏造证据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的做了那种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再叫一位参考人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因果为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能动手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都不得不回答那个人的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不得不隐藏起来的事情是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争开始之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时的JJ集团社长海胜麟六
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向警察局提议  要提供某个软件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个软件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以任意更改电脑文件的最后更新日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不留任何痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以改写没收的电子类文件日期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证明其有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  让她住口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软件只有海胜持有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察和检察院在他的协助下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对战时很多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:09:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord0\b1\fs12\fn@宋体\frz-90\c&HFFFFFF&\move(45,211,57,211,0,420)\clip(50,117,179,328)}警察厅  警备局  科长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再和海胜扯上关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉  变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会说谎的你说我在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么结成新十郎一定会推理出别天王的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是名侦探啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨江  我那时的确在家里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吞噬灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是新十郎说  不要杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不杀人而吞噬灵魂很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说不能再和我一起了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord0\b1\fs12\fn@宋体\frz-90\c&H000000&\move(32,142,44,142,0,420)\clip(37,53,156,252)}太阳能发电支持派·企业家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检察院还没有把那个杀人犯立案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:11:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还否认了篡改软件的存在不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸当天  不破先生您和海胜见过面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且立刻就
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  立刻就离开了座位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想起来  可能就是个替身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天来历不明的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看清楚了么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他上了电梯  可是哪里都…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胜先生  你认罪么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发明违法程序  杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胜先生  说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胜会长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有义务对国民解释清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去向各位老师表示谢意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胜先生  请回答我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胜先生  请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟警察的关系是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord0\b1\be0\3a&H8D\fs12\fn@宋体\frz-90\3c&H000000&\c&H000000&\move(437,132,450,132,0,420)\clip(443,31,548,232)}公共保安队·队员  水野的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和警察的私下交涉已经解决了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网上都在盛传  希望把你杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord0\b1\fs12\fn@宋体\frz-90\c&HFFFFFF&\move(328,163,342,163,0,420)\clip(334,78,478,260)}公共保安队·分队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胜  到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位请退后  汽车没法开出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险  请后退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胜先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胜先生  要逃走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去急救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自知无法逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了自杀准备了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家沉重地举行着守灵仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胜麟六为战后日本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作出了很大贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果海胜本人打算自杀的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么司机水野则是同行的无辜受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今  你还打算怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战败侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把他杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  是自杀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  遗体的DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和水野和海胜会长的DNA是一致的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了会长的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和…我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我究竟做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别天王在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种东西的踪迹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该在海胜身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太烦人了  你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在这里起争执
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我注意到的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲电脑里的数据已经被全部删除了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点痕迹也没留
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  可能是自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲是那种
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将身为保安的水野牵扯进去的人么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你了解我父亲么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是想要了解他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要知道他的真实面目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才帮助了侦探先生也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这样没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有意义？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相隐藏在人的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有许多不为人知的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫做因果的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  说来话长了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我也有很多无法对你讲的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲说过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定会推理出别天王的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然出现了两个海胜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必然会推理出那是别天王能力使然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次事件  实在实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请节哀顺变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想请会长做顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这位侦探先生说了奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪  哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果汽车爆炸不是自杀的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有嫌疑的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第一次爆炸中幸存的不破重次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和水野的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安分队长  三原保太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有从医院离开的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条手帕  是什么时候出现在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是因果最后一次来这里的时候留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那天白天的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把这条手帕给了代议员仓满美音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因果什么时候得到这条手帕的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说他见过仓满美音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里  什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起仓满议员  有一些有趣的情报哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与海胜一同去世的公共保安队的水野左近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是仓满议员大学时的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人的关系很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全看不出那种关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要入侵大学网络找出名册吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风守
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见到水野的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战败侦探  紧盯着海胜会长的不就是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这句
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往后一些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是特殊服务
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快点说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢岛先生的委托难得顺利解决了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢岛的委托  最终没有实现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以普通人并不知道这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那个家伙却知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an5\bord0\b1\fs12\fn@宋体\frz-90\c&H000000&\move(153,167,166,167,0,390)\clip(158,96,228,245)}盗版软件贩卖者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道关于那首歌的什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太老了  而且好像没有电子化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是特别老的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最近刚刚发行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被禁止发行了的夜长姬专辑的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候真是  怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an5\bord0\b1\fs12\fn@宋体\frz-90\c&H000000&\move(135,187,147,187,0,390)\clip(140,101,235,239)}安全责任员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an5\bord0\b1\fs12\fn@宋体\frz-90\c&H000000&\move(175,153,161,153,0,390)\clip(67,29,168,254)}东关东社会恢复促进中心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入这里对我来说也是个不错的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被女孩子包围着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还要找他干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是百忙之中抽空答应你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该是最清楚别天王的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别天王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是认为海胜麟六利用了别天王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.89,0:19:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伪装成死亡也很容易
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胜麟六还活着？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些全部是关于别天王的记录吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里规定  写小说是个人自由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord0\b1\fs12\fn@宋体\frz-90\c&H000000&\move(38,205,52,205,0,420)\clip(44,123,102,248)}犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然看到了那个之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我重复了关于那种能力的实验和记录
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以那种能力能够做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全部试了一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  那是我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:19:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个「生者与死者」是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是有趣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如这里有生者存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你们称为别天王的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要人相信那是尸体的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难成功
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生者会说话能活动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大脑通过视觉和听觉会接收到那些信息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那些信息与你从别天王那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到的故事是矛盾的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些矛盾会不断折磨大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如我在这想要假扮成「结城新十郎」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  因为真正的你就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大脑无法承受这矛盾的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  爆炸事件中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原形人物没有出现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  相关人士很容易认为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情跟自己想的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重点是要让他听到声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后别天王通过操纵视觉的认识使大脑里…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胜麟六利用别天王的能力杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还伪造了自己身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早送到事务所的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.36,0:21:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宴会的邀请函
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发信人是
